This is a project of 5 students from the University of Plovdiv, Bulgaria.
It is a try to create shader with many features showcasing the capabilities of glsl.

We use the Basic Ogre Framework as base project so we can focus on creating the shader.

http://www.ogre3d.org/
http://www.ogre3d.org/tikiwiki/tiki-index.php?page_ref_id=1627&pagenum=1

Build:
  -Linux:
      install ogre
      cd path_to_openUberShader
      cmake .
      make 
  -Windows:
      not tested yet